{"tha-ap382:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap382:0.2":"Bodhivandanavagga ","tha-ap382:0.3":"Kasumariphaladayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap382:1.1":"“Kanikaramva jotantam, ","tha-ap382:1.2":"nisinnam pabbatantare; ","tha-ap382:1.3":"Addasam virajam buddham, ","tha-ap382:1.4":"lokajettham narasabham. ","tha-ap382:2.1":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap382:2.2":"sire katvana anjalim; ","tha-ap382:2.3":"Kasumariphalam gayha, ","tha-ap382:2.4":"buddhasetthassadasaham. ","tha-ap382:3.1":"Ekattimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap382:3.2":"yam phalamadadim aham; ","tha-ap382:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap382:3.4":"phaladanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap382:4.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap382:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap382:4.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap382:5.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap382:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap382:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap382:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap382:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap382:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap382:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma kasumariphaladayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap382:8.1":"Kasumariphaladayakattherassapadanam dasamam. ","tha-ap382:9.1":"Bodhivandanavaggo atthatimsatimo. ","tha-ap382:10.1":"Tassuddanam ","tha-ap382:11.1":"Bodhi patali uppali, ","tha-ap382:11.2":"patti ca sattapanniyo; ","tha-ap382:11.3":"Gandhamutthi ca citako, ","tha-ap382:11.4":"talam sumanadamako; ","tha-ap382:11.5":"Kasumariphali ceva, ","tha-ap382:11.6":"gatha ekunasatthika. "}